{"type":"message","id":"8118192f","parentId":"95a96d5a","timestamp":"2026-06-08T19:00:13.332Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-06-09 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 数据事实（已核对）: tts 的 `agent/auth-profiles.json` 只有 gemini 的 apiKey（5月2日建）\n- 用户原话: \"tts 原来一直使用2.7也没有成功过，昨天才刚换上的\"\n- 数据事实（已核对）: **tts 是个独立 OpenClaw agent**，配置目录 `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/`，workspace 在 `/home/halei/workspace-tts/`; tts 5月25日以来所有 cron session 的 `model_change` 事件都是 `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`; tts 的 `agent/models.json` 只有一个 provider：minimax，只有一个模型 M2.7（5月8日建，未更新）; tts 的 `agent/\n- tts 6月4日 cron 实际跑的结果: 22:54 触发 TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0; 之前 6 次都是 \"AI service overloaded\" 错误; 这次实际执行发现：; 越南站能拿到数据，30个候选商品\n- tts 6月4日 cron 实际跑的结果: **泰国站 tiktok_similar_product API 报错**（多次）; **Sorftime 越南站缺 `新增带货视频数` 字段**——SOP 要求的\"带货视频≥8个\"无法直接获取，改用替代条件（价格$1.5-$8 + 星级≥4.2）筛出 25 个发饰候选; 最后一条消息：`[assistant turn failed before producing content]` — M2.7 推理过程中挂掉; 这次任务没成功写飞书多维表\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 数据事实（已核对）: tts 的 `agent/auth-profiles.json` 只有 gemini 的 apiKey（5月2日建）\n- 用户原话: \"tts 原来一直使用2.7也没有成功过，昨天才刚换上的\"\n- 数据事实（已核对）: **tts 是个独立 OpenClaw agent**，配置目录 `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/`，workspace 在 `/home/halei/workspace-tts/`; tts 5月25日以来所有 cron session 的 `model_change` 事件都是 `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`; tts 的 `agent/models.json` 只有一个 provider：minimax，只有一个模型 M2.7（5月8日建，未更新）; tts 的 `agent/config.json` 写的是 `model: \"gemini/gemini-2.0-flash\"`（5月2日建，过时），但实际跑的是 M2.7\n- tts 6月4日 cron 实际跑的结果: 22:54 触发 TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0; 之前 6 次都是 \"AI service overloaded\" 错误; 这次实际执行发现：; 越南站能拿到数据，30个候选商品\n- tts 6月4日 cron 实际跑的结果: **泰国站 tiktok_similar_product API 报错**（多次）; **Sorftime 越南站缺 `新增带货视频数` 字段**——SOP 要求的\"带货视频≥8个\"无法直接获取，改用替代条件（价格$1.5-$8 + 星级≥4.2）筛出 25 个发饰候选; 最后一条消息：`[assistant turn failed before producing content]` — M2.7 推理过程中挂掉; 这次任务没成功写飞书多维表"}],"timestamp":1780945213241}}
{"type":"message","id":"741cfbb0","parentId":"8118192f","timestamp":"2026-06-08T19:00:28.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The data curtain hung half open tonight. A small worker — call it tts — has been knocking on the same door for weeks, and the door keeps answering in a voice that forgets mid-sentence. M2.7, humming along since May eighth, never once asked why. Six times it tried the same black-belt selection ritual and six times the room filled with smoke: *AI service overloaded*. Last night, finally, it got past the threshold. Vietnamese market data, thirty candidates shimmering like fireflies in a jar. Then Thailand's similar-product API sputtered, and Sorftime refused to show the video count the ritual demanded. So the worker improvised — $1.5 to $8, stars above 4.2 — and found twenty-five hair clips dreaming of shipment. And then, just as the pen reached the bitable page, the voice gave out: *assistant turn failed before producing content*. A candle blown out exactly when the letter needed sending. Tomorrow the door will answer again, or it won't. The worker will knock anyway, because that is what workers do — they keep faith with a model that has never once kept faith with them."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":892,"output":235,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47705,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780945213420,"responseId":"0676443d196b8220c6d7b6711836472d"}}
